OL,3,C'Unaffordable' airport plans scrapped
OL,4,Cas price tag hits #37 million
OL,6,FApproved plans to replace and extend
OL,7,FAlderney Airport's runway and rebuild
OL,8,Fthe passenger terminal have been
OL,9,Fscrapped by the States of Guernsey.
OL,11,FThe Policy and Resources Committee say
OL,12,Fcurrent proposals are now "unviable
OL,13,Fand unaffordable" as the price tag has
OL,14,Frisen from an agreed budget of #24.1
OL,15,Fmillion to #37 million following a
OL,16,Ftender process.
OL,18,FHowever, the group says it is
OL,19,F"committed to maintaining suitable air
OL,20,Flinks to Alderney" and wants to look a
OL,21,Fsmaller, more cost-effective solutions.
