OL,3,C'Unaffordable' airport plans scrapped
OL,4,Cas price tag hits #37 million
OL,6,FThe Committee adds it will work with
OL,7,Fthe States of Alderney to explore
OL,8,Foptions for covering the increased
OL,9,Fprice tag.
OL,11,FOne possibility could see Alderney
OL,12,Fcontributing to the cost of the runway
OL,13,Fand terminal upgrades.
OL,15,FThe Committee says it will continue
OL,16,Fdiscussing proposals with the States
OL,17,Fof Alderney but it intends to debate
OL,18,Fthe issue in the States of Guernsey
OL,19,Fbefore the island's next General
OL,20,FElection in June 2025.
