OL,6,FAlderney residents and politicians
OL,7,Fhave expressed concerns about a
OL,8,Fcurrent lack of reliable air links
OL,9,Fwith Guernsey for healthcare, business
OL,10,Fand trade.
OL,12,FThe runway is currently covered with a
OL,13,Fpatchwork of temporary repairs.
OL,15,FHotel director Tracey Farquhar-Beck
OL,16,Fsays: "Shocked but not shocked is my
OL,17,Freaction, I'm very disappointed and
OL,18,Fworried.
