OL,4,Cas price tag hits #37 million
OL,6,F"If there isn't a resolution to this,
OL,7,Fif nothing happens, then the impact
OL,8,Fwill be terrible, devastating,
OL,9,Fespecially for tourism on Alderney. We
OL,10,Fhave enough problems as it is."
OL,12,FThe Chair of Policy and Finance for
OL,13,FAlderney States, Nigel Vooght, adds:
OL,14,F"It's already having an impact on
OL,15,Ftourism and business, when the runway
OL,16,Fhas to be repaired then you can't fly
OL,17,Fplanes there.
OL,19,F"We need to improve the runway so we
OL,20,Fcan help tourism and rebuild our
OL,21,Feconomy, it's vital."
